data.description: Home has enough room for your family and friends to be together comfortably, boasting 5 bedrooms & a large bonus room that could be a 6th bedroom and 2.75 bathrooms. Open concept living. Stainless appliances & the fridge stays! There is a rainier cherry tree as well as a plum tree in the front yard that give you delicious fruit when in season.
